docs.text: 邓朝钟. Undergraduate.           I'm a student majoring in Intelligent Science and Technology at the Liangjiang Artificial Intelligence College of Chongqing University of Technology.          Currently, I'm a senior exchange student at the College of Excellent Engineers of Chongqing University.          My graduation project is about the security of large models. If you have anything you'd like to discuss with me, feel free to reach out.
